{"lemma":"جَدِيرٌ","slug":"جَدِيرٌ","root":"ج.د.ر","root_slug":"ج-د-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-د-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n5217"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B1%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"fit, suitable"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"worthy, deserving"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"proper, appropriate"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"afflicted with smallpox"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"walled in"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare جَدُرَ (jadura, “to be suitable, to be worthy”), جِدَار (jidār, “wall”), جُدِرَ (judira, “to have smallpox”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n5217","headword_ar":"جَدِيرٌ","root":"jdr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A place"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having a wall built around it; a walled"},{"kind":"text","text":"place. (S, K.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mujad~arN","text_ar":"مُجَدَّرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Adapted, disposed, apt, meet, suited, suitable, fitted, fit, proper, competent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"worthy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaliyqN","text_ar":"خَلِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaqiyqN","text_ar":"حَقِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) fem. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) pl. mase."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadiyruwna","text_ar":"جَدِيرُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"judaraA='u","text_ar":"جُدَرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) pl. fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadiyraAtN","text_ar":"جَدِيرَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadaAy^iru","text_ar":"جَدَايِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa jadiyrN bika*aA","text_ar":"هُوَ جَدِيرٌ بِكَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lika*aA","text_ar":"لِكَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is adapted, disposed, apt, meet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for such a thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb;) and ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"naturally"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drawn to it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 707.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anota jadiyrN A^ano","text_ar":"اَنْتَ جَدِيرٌ اَنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafoEala ka*aA","text_ar":"تَفْعَلَ كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thou art adapted, disposed, apt, meet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for doing such a thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"worthy to do it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano yafoEala","text_ar":"اَنْ يَفْعَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu lamajodarapN","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَمَجْدَرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and in like manner you say of two persons, and of more, (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majoduwrN","text_ar":"مَجْدُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is one who is adapted, disposed, apt, meet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for doing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[such a thing]; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"worthy to do"},{"kind":"text","text":"[it]; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxolaqapN","text_ar":"مَخْلَقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) [↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majodarapN","text_ar":"مَجْدَرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"properly signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing, an affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a person, adapted, disposed, apt, meet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxolaqapN","text_ar":"مَخْلَقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHoraApN","text_ar":"مَحْرَاةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majoduwrN","text_ar":"مَجْدُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"called, adapted"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disposed"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., though said by Aboo-Jaafar Er-Ru- ásee to be a pass. part. n. having no verb.] Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi*`lika","text_ar":"بِذٰلِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahaA lamajodarapN","text_ar":"اـِنَّهَا لَمَجْدَرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily she is one who is adapted, disposed, apt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for that:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA^ano","text_ar":"بِاَنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafoEala *`lika","text_ar":"تَفْعَلَ ذٰلِكَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for doing that:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in like manner you say of two persons, and of more. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"li*aAka","text_ar":"لِذَاكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA AlA^amoru majodarapN","text_ar":"هٰذَا الاَمْرُ مَجْدَرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing, is one that is adapted, apt, meet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for that;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHoraApN","text_ar":"مَحْرَاةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA AlA^amoru majodarapN","text_ar":"هٰذَا الاَمْرُ مَجْدَرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohu","text_ar":"مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing, is one that is adapted, apt, meet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for him to do;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. he is adapted, apt, meet, &c., for doing it. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Msb","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}